'''''Dandi''''' was a [[Xiytiar-class heavy transport|''Xiytiar''-class heavy transport]] delivering comm arrays to [[Bretie Facility]] as part of the [[TIE Experimental Project]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], shortly after the [[Battle of Hoth/Legends|Battle of Hoth]]. It was accompanied by its sister ship, the ''[[Vrexlir]]''.

